  <sect2 id="install-aboot" role="installation">
    <title>Installation of aboot</title>

    <para os="aa">The following patches addresses build issues with GCC 4.x:</para>

<screen os="ab"><userinput>patch -Np1 -i ../&aboot-alpha-patch;</userinput></screen>

    <para>Compile the package:</para>

<screen><userinput>make</userinput></screen>

    <para>Install the package:</para>

<screen><userinput>make install</userinput></screen>

